<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 22:07:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>监管机构猛烈抨击家庭长达数周的等待以色列社会服务部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</link><description>家庭需要等待数周甚至数月才能从社会事务部机构获得帮助，认为对孩子构成风险的父母可以与他们举行监督会议，部分原因是大多数机构的工作时间少于要求的时间</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 21:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-17/ty-article/.premium/watchdog-slams-families-weeks-long-wait-for-israels-social-services-ministry/00000190-bcc8-de8b-adfc-bde88be50000</guid></item><item><title>为什么这名以色列裔美国人质的父母在共和党大会上发言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</link><description>奥马尔·诺伊特拉（Omer Neutra）在加沙被扣为人质已有九个多月了，他们的父母罗南·诺伊特拉（Ronen Neutra）和奥纳·诺伊特拉（Orna Neutra）说，“我们有发言权，我们将与美国人民对话，并要求他们加入我们的战斗。”两人表示，他们的讲话旨在让美国人牢记人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-israeli-american-hostages-parents-are-speaking-at-gop-convention/00000190-bcd3-de8b-adfc-bdf3957b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼部长报道了士兵因杀害哈马斯恐怖分子而被捕后自杀的虚假故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</link><description>奥兹玛·耶胡迪特议员写道，“追捕我们英雄士兵的检察官办公室不是国家检察官办公室，而是敌人的检察官办公室。”一旦发现该故事是虚假的，该帖子就被删除了</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 19:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-minister-reports-fake-story-about-solider-committing-suicide-after-arrest/00000190-bcdb-d3a7-a79e-fedbc9270000</guid></item><item><title>JD Vance 对以色列的立场如何？无论特朗普告诉他去哪里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</link><description>任何参与其中的人都应该问自己：当万斯无人跟随时会发生什么？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 18:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-16/ty-article/.highlight/where-will-j-d-vance-stand-on-israel-wherever-trump-tells-him-to/00000190-bca4-db2d-ab90-befef57a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层，14,000名特工人员死伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</link><description>以军认为，哈马斯陷入人力危机，对战地武装力量的指挥控制能力正在削弱，武装分子和指挥官的动机出现“裂痕”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership-14-000-operatives-killed-or-wounded/00000190-bc9c-db47-abb0-befd45310000</guid></item><item><title>以色列盟友警告称，由于财政部长斯莫特里奇在西岸的政策，西方将针对定居活动人士实施新的制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</link><description>被认为相对亲以色列的戴维·拉米本周作为英国外交大臣首次访问以色列，他在与以色列领导人的所有会晤中都提出了这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:29:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-allies-warn-of-new-western-sanctions-over-smotrichs-actions/00000190-bbd8-db47-abb0-bbf9bcc60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 284 天：以色列军队称其杀死了哈马斯一半的军事领导层</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人称，以色列国防军袭击了近东救济工程处学校，造成 15 人死亡。以色列国防军称，恐怖分子在此活动。 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：加沙南部汗尤尼斯有 17 人死亡。枪击案 ■ 以色列人因涉嫌为伊朗工作而被捕 ■ 战争进入 284 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 17:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-284-israeli-army-says-it-killed-half-of-hamas-military-leadership/00000190-bc80-d458-a3d7-bfe7f9e10000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯关押在加沙的以色列女兵的家人发布了被囚禁第一天的新照片</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</link><description>照片显示，阿甘·伯杰、丹妮拉·吉尔博亚、利里·阿尔巴格、纳马·利维和卡琳娜·阿里耶夫在加沙地带的一间公寓内受伤。据军方消息人士称，这些照片是几周前在加沙地带的一次行动中发现的</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:25:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-women-soldiers-held-by-hamas-release-photos-from-captivity/00000190-bc16-db47-abb0-be779d310000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特起诉以色列人，据称该人被伊朗在网上招募从事反国家行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</link><description>21 岁的 Elimelech Stern 是以色列中部城市贝特谢梅什的居民，据称伊朗情报部门在网上联系并要求他执行悬挂横幅、藏匿金钱和运送包裹等“任务”，以换取报酬，随后被捕。加密货币支付</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:52:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-to-indict-israeli-allegedly-recruited-by-iran-to-commit-acts-against-state/00000190-bbd9-d211-a5da-ffdbe2140000</guid></item><item><title>一场巨大的欺诈使以色列数亿美元的养老金被抹去。国家什么都不做</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</link><description>资本市场管理局承认，近一年来，在其监管下的养老金中，有数亿谢克尔被盗，但没有一个受害者被告知。但接受指责是另一回事</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-huge-fraud-erased-hundreds-of-millions-of-israeli-pensions-the-state-wont-protect-them/00000190-bb65-db47-abb0-bb7556920001</guid></item><item><title>以色列公设辩护律师：战时紧急立法严重侵犯囚犯权利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</link><description>根据公设辩护人办公室 2023 年活动报告，自以色列与加沙哈马斯战争爆发以来，提起的恐怖主义煽动起诉数量比过去四年还要多，同时对警察暴行的投诉也激增</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:06:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/public-defender-emergency-legislation-during-the-war-infringes-on-rights-of-prisoners/00000190-bb73-de8b-adfc-bb73ea3c0000</guid></item><item><title>数万名阿拉伯人住在耶路撒冷，没有自来水：“它将成为第二个加沙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</link><description>耶路撒冷最大的城区缺乏自来水，似乎没有人关心：Kafr Aqab 的居民每周只能获得几个小时的水，无法洗衣服或洗地板，被迫放弃淋浴</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-arabs-living-in-jerusalem-without-running-water-it-will-become-a-second-gaza/00000190-bb83-db81-a3f7-fb9fe9680000</guid></item><item><title>位智前首席执行官：“如果我们采取正确的步骤，新加坡将像我们旁边的加沙一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</link><description>以色列科技界最成功的人物之一诺姆·巴丁 (Noam Bardin) 在美国工作 13 年后于 10 月 7 日后的第二天返回以色列。“这场巨大的危机为这个国家提供了一个‘重启’的机会，尽管代价高昂。” ，”他告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-we-take-the-right-steps-singapore-will-look-like-gaza-next-to-us/00000190-b1bc-df47-a7bf-b1be45b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军告诉高等法院：许多坦克在战争中受损，弹药短缺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</link><description>针对女兵要求被允许在战斗岗位服役的请愿书，以色列军队回复称，由于战争，将推迟将女性编入装甲部队，该计划将于 2025 年 11 月启动</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 12:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-tells-high-court-many-tanks-damaged-in-the-war-there-is-ashortage-in-ammunition/00000190-bb29-de8b-adfc-bb298b860000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：如果没有以色列，世界上每个犹太人都将面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</link><description>拜登加强了对以色列的立场，称自己是犹太复国主义者。 “你不必是犹太人才能成为犹太复国主义者，”他在周一的采访中说。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/biden-without-israel-every-jew-in-the-world-would-be-at-risk/00000190-bac9-d458-a3d7-bbefa3f00000</guid></item><item><title>有一段时间，加沙人希望战争能够结束。现在他们感觉自己被抛弃了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</link><description>加沙人民说，世界只关心穆罕默德·德伊夫发生了什么，“没有人再谈论数十名死者了”。一位人权活动人士表示，过去曾有国际压力，但“现在，每个人都在等待内塔尼亚胡”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/for-a-moment-gazans-had-hope-the-war-would-end-now-they-feel-theyve-been-abandoned/00000190-bab2-d211-a5da-fffb31440000</guid></item><item><title>阻止向加沙提供援助的极右团体获得美国和以色列的免税捐款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</link><description>尽管受到制裁，三个极端民族主义团体仍从美国和以色列收到了超过 20 万美元的免税捐款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 09:06:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/far-right-groups-blocking-aid-to-gaza-receive-tax-deductible-donations-from-us-and-israel/00000190-ba8f-db47-abb0-baffc7370000</guid></item><item><title>人质交易的框架仍然存在。细节等待以色列领导人的意见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</link><description>现在重要的问题不是哈马斯领导人穆罕默德·德伊夫是生还是死，而是谈判将会发生什么。僵局可能会持续到美国大选，从而进一步危及人质的生命安全，并大大增加以色列和黎巴嫩之间爆发全面战争的可能性</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/a-framework-for-a-hostage-deal-still-exists-the-details-await-israels-leaders-input/00000190-ba57-d458-a3d7-bbf7ad6a0000</guid></item><item><title>三名军官和一名哲学家：决定谁是依良心拒服兵役者的秘密以色列国防军委员会内部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</link><description>人权倡导者表示，根据以色列国防军对该术语的定义，即使是马丁·路德·金和圣雄甘地也不会被视为良心拒服兵役者。委员会中的学者、活动人士、反对者和律师告诉《国土报》，军事系统如何应对挑衅的拒绝者</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:12:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/three-officers-and-a-philosopher-inside-the-secretive-idf-conscience-committee/00000190-b619-df08-a9fe-f7d9b7c10000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太艺术家对美化哈马斯大屠杀的艺术作品感到愤怒，感到沉默和疏远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</link><description>当纽约一个著名的文化空间向一位艺术家展示其橱窗并对哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击表示赞赏时，许多犹太和以色列艺术家感到震惊，但并不完全感到惊讶。正如一位策展人所指责的那样，艺术界是否创造了“一个从单一角度看待现实的平坦领域”？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</guid></item></channel></rss>